Name: RUNWAY COMPOSITION
Explanation: THE MATERIAL OF WHICH THE RUNWAY IS MADE.

Name: TYPE OF MATERIEL
Explanation: TYPE OF MATERIEL REQUIRED FOR MILITARY PURPOSES, EXCLUDING EQUIPMENT.

Name: TARGET MATERIAL TYPE
Explanation: THE TYPE OF MATERIAL FROM WHICH THE TARGET IS MADE.

Name: WASTE MATERIAL
Explanation: THE TYPE OF WASTE MATERIAL A SUPPLY SHIP IS ABLE TO RECEIVE.

Name: TYPE OF MATERIAL TO TRANSFER
Explanation: THE TYPE OF MATERIAL HELD FOR TRANSFER TO THE SPECIFIED UNIT.

Name: SURFACE MATERIAL
Explanation: THIS FIELD INDICATES THE MATERIAL LAYER CONSTITUTING THE EXTERIOR FACE OF AN OBJECT.

Name: MATERIAL, GENERAL
Explanation: INDICATES THE SUBSTANCE OR SUBSTANCES OUT OF WHICH AN ENTITY IS MADE.
